items.title: Ripe for Disruption: Opportunities and challenges in the evolving insurance sector
items.description: The insurance sector offers significant growth potential despite challenges like outdated underwriting, trust issues, and complex processes. Opportunities exist in areas such as vehicle underwriting, SMB insurance, and surety bonds, with innovation-driven startups poised to capitalise on these gaps.
